      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at getting my first house soon and i'm kinda confused about the different mortgage types. can u explain the difference between a fixed-rate mortgage and an adjustable-rate mortgage (arm)? specifically i want to know how the interest rate changes might affect my monthly payments over the first 5 years. thanks",
